Package: aisdk
Title: AI SDK for R - Unified Interface for AI Model Providers
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yonghe", "Xia", , "xiayh17@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A production-grade AI SDK for R featuring a layered architecture
    (Specification, Utilities, Providers, Core), middleware support, robust
    error handling with exponential backoff, support for multiple AI model
    providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.), local SLM inference, distributed MCP
    ecosystem, autonomous data science pipelines with self-healing code execution,
    and a global skill store for sharing AI capabilities.
